Class ScenarioConstant

  • java.lang.Object
    • ohos.distributedschedule.scenario.ScenarioConstant

  • public final class ScenarioConstant

    Provides a series of static constants representing various distributed scenario types.

    These constants are generally used as the value of the input parameter for ScenarioInfo#setScenarioType(int). Currently, only the navigation migration scenario type specified by SCENARIO_TYPE_NAVIGATION_CONTINUE is supported. If an unsupported scenario type is used, scenario registration will fail.
